Fix: set __session cookie synchronously before navigation

The cookie was only being set in AuthProvider's onAuthStateChanged
callback, which fires asynchronously. The login/signup handlers called
router.push() before the cookie existed, causing middleware to redirect
back to /login. Now the cookie is set immediately after getIdToken()
in both login and signup handlers, before navigating.

Co-Authored-By: Oz <oz-agent@warp.dev>
